{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6711","heading":"Failure by tax-exempt organization to disclose that certain information or service available from Federal Government","label":"6711 Failure by tax-exempt organization to disclose that certain information or service available from Federal Government","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/stF/ch68/schB/ptI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 100–203, title X, § 10705(c)101 Stat. 1330–464Dec. 22, 1987“The amendments made by this section [enacting this section] shall apply to offers and solicitations after .”January 31, 1988"],"amendments":["Effective Date, , , provided that:Pub. L. 100–203, title X, § 10705(c)101 Stat. 1330–464Dec. 22, 1987“The amendments made by this section [enacting this section] shall apply to offers and solicitations after .”January 31, 1988"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Imposition of penalty","label":"a Imposition of penalty","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a tax-exempt organization offers to sell (or solicits money for) specific information or a routine service for any individual which could be readily obtained by such individual free of charge (or for a nominal charge) from an agency of the Federal Government,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the tax-exempt organization, when making such offer or solicitation, fails to make an express statement (in a conspicuous and easily recognizable format) that the information or service can be so obtained, and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such failure is due to intentional disregard of the requirements of this subsection,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Amount of penalty","label":"b Amount of penalty","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"$1,000, or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"50 percent of the aggregate cost of the offers and solicitations referred to in subsection (a)(1) which occurred on such day and with respect to which there was such a failure.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Definitions","label":"c Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Tax-exempt organization","label":"1 Tax-exempt organization","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is described in subsection (c) or (d) of section 501 and exempt from taxation under section 501(a), or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is a political organization (as defined in section 527(e)).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Day on which failure occurs","label":"2 Day on which failure occurs","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6711/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft26%2Fs6711%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The day on which any failure referred to in subsection (a) occurs shall be determined under rules similar to the rules of section 6710(d).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
